---
title: Carb Smart Double Chicken and Dijon Sauce with Apple-Walnut Salad
description: Tender chicken breasts and buttery Dijon sauce are a match made in French cuisine heaven! We've paired them with spinach, apple and walnut salad tossed in a simple vinaigrette. Eating light never tasted so good!

